PEER ASSESSMENT OF PROJECT EORK
YOUR PROJECT WORK CARRIES 16 points ( 10 points go to Credit, 6 points go to the Course work)

Dear Students, please send me PERSONALLY the Peer-Assessment of all your teammates

   1 I give you up to 8,5 points for your participation and work 

 2. You assess your group members from -2,5  to +7,5 depending on the following criteria

  - communication with group members

  - contribution to the group work

  - keeping to the schedule

Then I add numbers ( assessment of all group members) and find the avarage of it,  and you've got your final score (up to 16 points). Please assess your groupmates objectively. If you give someone a low score , please explain in IN A FEW WORDS. If I have further questions connected with your assessment, I will contact you. 

For example:

Lisa Pishina     (7,5)
Kate Rudyk      (- 2,5) and so on.
